      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BORACAY STORM (5) has a strong record this trip with 13 wins and 12 placings from 31 starts. Recorded a 4 length win (25.28) in a Mix 5 last time at Q Lakeside. With a clean break looks hard to beat. NACHO PROBLEM (2) missed the frame last time, finishing 7th (25.75) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Great record here at the trip having never missed the frame including one win. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from three starts. Worth another chance. BUCK SHINES (1) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at Shepparton over 450m behind Paw Welkes (26.27) in a Grade 5. Should be about the money. PLAY LAB (7) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
